headline: Costco pulls a popular product line from its warehouse shelves

headline: Is T-Mobile US Stock Underperforming the Nasdaq?
summary: Although T-Mobile US has lagged behind the broader Nasdaq Composite over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain moderately optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
